%hr/

.row.product-details
  .col-md-4
    = image_tag("what.png", :alt => "What is Liberatio?", :class => "pull-left", :style => "padding-right: 15px;")
    %h4.text-liberatio-primary.cursive What is Liberatio?
    %h5 Liberatio is a cloud-based systems management tool designed to give you greater control and insight over your IT devices and infrastructure. Agents are a key component that, when deployed on your devices, enable real-time, two-way communication and management securely over the Web.

  .col-md-4
    = image_tag("who.png", :alt => "Who is Liberatio for?", :class => "pull-left", :style => "padding-right: 15px;")
    %h4.text-liberatio-primary.cursive Who is Liberatio for?
    %h5 IT Managers, IT guys, and System Administrators who need to get a handle on their IT infrastructure. Liberatio works well in small to mid-size environments, and can be used to manage from just one to 1000+ devices. Liberatio works securely over the Web, and requires no firewall or network modifications.

  .col-md-4
    = image_tag("do.png", :alt => "What can Liberatio do?", :class => "pull-left", :style => "padding-right: 15px;")
    %h4.text-liberatio-primary.cursive What can Liberatio do?
    %h5 Liberatio enables you to streamline your IT infrastructure by improving the way you manage your devices. Automatic hardware and software inventory, real-time communication, and continual monitoring will not only help you resolve issues, but also prevent them from occuring.